@startuml doc-relationships
!theme plain
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F3E5F5
}

title Document Relationships (from Traceability Tables)

package "🟦 Static Baseline" {
  [Intended Use]
  [Classification]
}

package "🟨 Dynamic Upstream" {
  [Risk File]
  [UX File]
  [Cyber File]
  [AI Docs]
  [Clinical Eval]
}

rectangle "🟢 SRS\n(Central Hub)" as SRS

package "Downstream" {
  [Architecture]
  [V&V Plans]
  [IFU]
  [Tech Doc]
}

[Intended Use] --> SRS : scope/claims
[Classification] --> SRS : risk level
[Risk File] --> SRS : controls
[UX File] --> SRS : UI reqs
[Cyber File] --> SRS : security
[AI Docs] --> SRS : perf targets

SRS ..> [Risk File] : 🔴 safety changes
SRS ..> [UX File] : 🔴 UI changes
SRS ..> [Cyber File] : 🔴 security
SRS ..> [AI Docs] : 🔴 algo changes
SRS --> [Architecture] : primary driver
SRS --> [V&V Plans] : 🔴 test cases

note right of SRS
  SRS Review Agent monitors
  changes here → notifies owners
end note

@enduml
